soterik um und wie greift die politische Bildung das Thema auf? Die Fachtagung \"Esoterik und Demokratie \u2013 Ein Spannungsverh\u00e4ltnis\" machte sich vom 5.-6. September 2022 in Fulda und online auf die kontroverse Suche nach Antworten.Erscheinungsdatum:", "language": null, "image": "https://www.bpb.de/cache/images/4/754154_teaser_3x2_800.jpg?1984E", "pagetype": "article", "links": ["#skip-nav-target", "/", "/die-bpb/ueber-uns/informationen-in-leichter-sprache/", "/die-bpb/ueber-uns/gebaerdensprache/", "/die-bpb/ueber-uns/federal-agency-for-civic-education/", "/shop/zeitschriften/apuz/", "/shop/zeitschriften/izpb/", "https://www.fluter.de", "https://www.eurotopics.net", "https://www.hanisauland.de", "https://www.spielbar.de", "https://www.kinofenster.de", "/themen/politisches-system/politik-einfach-fuer-alle/", "/themen/deutschlandarchiv/", "/shop/zeitschriften/apuz/228/aus-politik-und-zeitgeschichte-alt/", "/shop/zeitschriften/izpb/229/informationen-zur-politischen-bildung-alt/", "https://www.fluter.de", "https://www.eurotopics.net", "https://www.hanisauland.de", "https://www.spielbar.de", "https://www.kinofenster.de", "/", "/die-bpb/ueber-uns/informationen-in-leichter-sprache/", "/die-bpb/ueber-uns/informationen-in-leichter-sprache/", "/die-bpb/ueber-uns/federal-agency-for-civic-education/", "/merkliste/", "/shop/warenkorb/?status=shoppingCard", "/die-bpb/ueber-uns/service/impressum/", "/die-bpb/ueber-uns/service/kontakt/", "/die-bpb/ueber-uns/service/269718/datenschutzerklaerung-fuer-bpb-de/", "https://www.facebook.com/bpb.de", "https://social.bund.de/@bpb", "https://twitter.com/bpb_de", "https://www.instagram.com/bpb_de/", "https://www.youtube.com/user/bpbtv", "/die-bpb/ueber-uns/informationen-in-leichter-sprache/", "/die-bpb/ueber-uns/informationen-in-leichter-sprache/", "/die-bpb/ueber-uns/federal-agency-for-civic-education/", "/merkliste/", "/shop/warenkorb/?status=shoppingCard", "/die-bpb/ueber-uns/service/impressum/", "/die-bpb/ueber-uns/service/kontak